thalai nagaram ( tamil : தலைநகரம் ) is a 2006 tamil film directed by suraj . the film stars director sundar c and jyothimayi . this film was a low-budget production and the soundtrack was composed by d. imman . this story is a tale of a man who sacrifices his life to kick out gangsters ruining others lives . it also stars vadivelu , prakash raj and bose venkat among others . it enjoyed huge success . the soundtrack was a great hit and the song " etho nennukiren " charted at the top position for 1 week . it completed 100 days . it 's a successful remake of priyadarshan-mohanlal starrer abhimanyu . it was remade in kannada as devru .